high_descs: Turn around and go near the cabinet table.
Take the silver colored statue from the cupboard of the table.
Turn around and go to the next desk.
Put the statue on the desk.
Turn around and go near the bed.
Take another statue from the bed.
Turn around and go near the desk.
Put the statue on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Collect the statue and placed it on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight to the cabinet area, then turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the statue from the cabinets beneath the kitchen sink.
Turn around and head for the door that is ahead and slightly to the left, entering the bedroom, then take the right into the closet.
Place the statue on top of the desk in the closet.
Turn around back into the bedroom, and go towards the bed.
Pick up the statue from the bed.
Return to the desk in the closet.
Place the second statue down on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place two statues on a closet desk.

high_descs: Turn around and head right to reach the cabinet under the sink.
Pick up the statue from the cabinet.
Turn around and turn left to walk to the bedroom across the passage and turn right to reach the desk.
Put the statue on the desk.
Turn around to reach the bed.
Pick up the statue from the bed.
Turn around to reach the desk.
Put the statue on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put two statues on the desk.
